        i^{45}







        (1+i)+\overline{(1+i)}

Convert the following complex numbers to the form a + bi.






        2 e^{\pi / 6}







        5 e^{9\pi/4}







        3 e^{\pi}







        \frac{1}{2}e^{7\pi/4}

Calculate each of the following expressions.






        (1+i)^{-1}







        (1 - i)^{6}







        (\sqrt{3} + i)^{5}







        (-i)^{10}







        ((1-i)/2)^{4}







        (-\sqrt{2} - \sqrt{2}\, i)^{12}







